Common Information
1) Url : https://www.saucedemo.com/
2) Test ID : standard_user, locked_out_user, problem_user, performance_glitch_user
3) Password : secret_sauce

Tool Box Module
1) Class Setup : Used to setup a browser connectivity and open a url
2) Function get_data : Used to get test data from CSV file and create an output file with the status

Reporting Module
1) Create test count of the entire run of testcases
2) Plot a pie-chart with the details of Pass, Fail, Blocked, Not Run

Snapshot Module
1) Takes a full screen screen-shot of the active page
2) By default it is configured to take snapshot of only Test failures.

Testcases
1) Test_001 : First Testcase
2) Test_002 : Second Testcase
3) Test_003 ... and so on